---
// src/pages/services/cooktop-repair/burner-not-igniting.astro
// Wave 3b — failure-mode sub-service under residential cooktop pillar.
// SEO: "gas cooktop burner not lighting", "stove burner won't ignite",
// "gas cooktop clicking no flame", "cooktop spark module".
// Practitioner: ~30% of "won't light" calls resolve at $89 dx with no parts
