    <p class="price-note">Residential $89 diagnostic, applied toward repair. About 30% of these calls resolve at the diagnostic with no additional parts.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">08 · Why us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Six reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
